WEBVTT

00:04:28.221 --> 00:04:31.146
Kama ukishindwa, unakufa.

00:04:31.146 --> 00:04:33.490
Hippomenes alimshinda vipi?

00:04:33.490 --> 00:04:35.416
Alikua na matofaa madogo ya dhahabu,

00:04:35.416 --> 00:04:38.034
na angekimbia mbele, na kuangusha
tofaa dogo la dhahabu.

00:04:38.034 --> 00:04:40.058
Angempita, na kuangusha tofaa la dhahabu.

00:04:40.058 --> 00:04:44.284
Akaendelea kukengeushwa. Hatimae
akashinda mbio.

00:04:44.284 --> 00:04:47.514
Kumbuka tu kusudi haya matofaa
madogo ya dhahabu

00:04:47.514 --> 00:04:50.086
yanakuja na kukufikia na unataka kuzituma

00:04:50.086 --> 00:04:53.922
au kuzitwiti au kutuma ujumbe
usiku wa manane.

00:04:53.922 --> 00:04:57.170
Na kisha, bila shaka, kuna Narcissus.

00:04:57.170 --> 00:05:00.717
Hakuna mtu hapa anaweza kutuhumiwa
au kumjua Narcissus.